      • getState

        public String getState()
        A string with one of the following values: 'none', 'pending', 'viewable', 'error' and 'success'. none - the unknown or initial state. pending - content is being generated but is not ready yet. viewable - like pending, though indicates that enough content is available to be useful. error - an error happened and this content is not available. success - all of the content is available and complete.
        Returns:
        state
